name: Powerball DAO
description:
Let's win Powerball lottery! 
There are 11,238,513 five number combinations in the Powerball Lottery.  To win the jackpot you also have to match 1 of 26 "powerballs" making your chances 1 in 292,201,338.

Hypothetically if 112.38513 people were able to buy 2,600,000 tickets each, one of them is guaranteed to win the jackpot. 
So 1123.8513 people would have to buy 260000 tickets each, 11238.513 need 26000 tickets, 112385.13 need 2600 tickets and 1123851.3 people need only 260 tickets each.   

Here's the plan.  
1. Randomly distribute all 11,238,513 five number combinations to members of the Powerball DAO (1 set of numbers per token purchased).  

2. Each member will be responsible for preparing 26 Powerball tickets per token owned. For example if you buy 1 token you will be expected to buy 26 tickets (one for each of the 26 Powerballs and your 5 number set).  

4. DAO members will vote on a future Powerball drawing date and all play their tickets at the same time. 

5. Jackpot!
payDisclosure: 90% of the funds raised will be deposited to a multi-sig wallet and used to develop, market and manage the DAO subject to voting rules established by the DAO.  The remaining 10% will be deposited to the project owner.
